<doc id="614019" wikidata="Q1759660" url="?curid=614019" title="Battle of Changsha (1941)">
<text>The (Second) Battle of Changsha (6 September – 8 October 1941; ) was Japan&#x27;s second attempt at taking the city of Changsha, China, the capital of Hunan Province, as part of the Second Sino-Japanese War.

The Japanese were repulsed again, and the battle ended with a Chinese victory.

==See also==
*Battle of Changsha (1939)
*Battle of Changsha (1941–1942)
*Battle of Changsha (1944)
*&quot;Battle of Changsha&quot; (TV series), the TV series depicting this event

